{"tid":2020254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"527 國歌法二讀 - 係咪真係仲要圍立法會?","createTime":"2020-05-17T02:27:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T09:57:37.000Z","uid":334720,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2df951d707f0204b823a18f096958c76ef7cd8a6","tid":2020254,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T02:27:20.000Z","msg":"係咪真係仲要去圍堵立法會? 成本效益極低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能你地會問: 咁係咪咩都唔做呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我目前能夠比既建議都係: 倒不如將所有我地既人數放哂去幫全港商場提早關門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去圍又做唔到對政府實際傷害, 經濟攬炒唔係大家其中一個共識?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">即使527重現612咁樣, 只會仲衰過612, 我保證未夠人就直接TG 水炮 圍捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0N4hQDu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0N4hQDu.png&h=08be3fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而你知道圍立法會其實都係期待有勇武進化，但有無諗過佢地一但出事係完全得不償失？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同音樂椅一樣，差在你好彩唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你試過親眼望到d事發生，你就會更加深明點解我咁諗<br />\n唔好再覺得有勇武就乜都成事<br />\n全民勇武無可能，鼓吹部份勇武=over their dead body<br />\n利申：非分化，只係唔想大家繼續有個心態係鼓吹勇武<br />\n<br />\n大家記得個目標係5大訴求, 針對既係政府管治有問題<br />\n唔好成日話咩要打狗同佢地博過, 咪撚玩啦伍寶<br />\n因為大家都知佔領 / 圍堵 / 陣地 完算唔划算, 所以先有和你shop <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次狗隊一入場 市民即刻散水, 衰D講句, 就算有人被捕 都已經係效益高過圍立法會<br />\n<br />\n如果527 仲係好似612咁去圍立法會, 你認為D狗真係可以好似上年咁, 去到下晝先搞9你?<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/16/Repetitive_error.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/350?cb=20070902105305\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F16%2FRepetitive_error.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F350%3Fcb%3D20070902105305&h=695bb77f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知你地睇左721份報告未, 不斷講咩資訊量龐大, 難以歸納來龍去脈, 加上主要抗爭地點係上環, 所以元朗好少狗<br />\n<br />\n代表D咩? 代表如果單一地點, 佢地好易包圍去驅散, 但多一地點, 佢地未必support到"},{"pid":"ecea932040bbcb6f7ae37bea01e924b638256313","tid":2020254,"uid":334720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T02:28:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><ins>大家睇埋下面呢2個POST既分析</ins></strong></span><br />\n有無人可以話比我聽，點解仲要佔領、陣地、再被包圍？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2018414/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2018414/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n本身我係支持勇武抗爭的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2020000/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2020000/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><br />\n<strong><ins>現有既行動POST</ins></strong></span><br />\n（長文）（置頂）(戰術）金鐘野餐攻略 沙盤推演<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2018117/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2018117/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[行動］527 全民野餐日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2017976/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2017976/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"035ec035405e4d02bc05f0bcaa8c2842688ab6a7","tid":2020254,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T02:29:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f1d483127f3c923b120328ce87d2e3f8528a20db","tid":2020254,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T02:30:32.000Z","msg":"應該入都入唔到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1531eaf1142e7953e84aab5ef17ec3da4913d57","tid":2020254,"uid":341302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T02:31:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2ed0831dd17e1e8a5593405ad1829666ee7cda","tid":2020254,"uid":104032,"like":0,"di